'''伊萨姆·沙拉夫''' ({{lang-ar|عصام عبد العزيز شرف}}, {{IPA-arz|ʕeˈsˤɑːm ʕæbdelʕæˈziːz ʃɑɾˤɑf|IPA}}，{{bd|1952年||}}) 是一名埃及学者和政治家。2004年到2005年曾任埃及运输部长，2011年3月3日到12月7日担任[[埃及总理|埃及总理]]。

== 早年与教育 ==
1952年他生于[[吉萨|吉萨]]<ref name="Ahram">{{cite web|title=Meet Essam Sharaf: Egypt's first post-revolution Prime Minister|url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/~/NewsContent/1/64/6892/Egypt/Politics-/Meet-Essam-Sharaf-Egypts-first-postrevolution-Prim.aspx|publisher=Ahram online|accessdate=4 March 2011|coauthors=Ahmed Elieba & Marwa Hussein|archive-date=2011-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110305225558/http://english.ahram.org.eg/~/NewsContent/1/64/6892/Egypt/Politics-/Meet-Essam-Sharaf-Egypts-first-postrevolution-Prim.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1975年获得[[开罗大学|开罗大学]][[土木工程|土木工程]]专业[[理学士|理学士]]，后来到美国[[普渡大學|普渡大學]]继续深造，并分别于1980年和1984年获得硕士和博士学位<ref name="purdue">{{cite web |url=https://engineering.purdue.edu/Engr/People/Awards/Institutional/DEA/DEA_2006/sharaf |title=Purdue University Profile of Essam Sharaf |accessdate=3 March 2011 |archive-date=2021-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212100339/https://engineering.purdue.edu/Engr/People/Awards/Institutional/DEA/DEA_2006/sharaf }}</ref>。

== 政治观点 ==
他强烈反对埃及与[[以色列|以色列]]关系正常化。他认为结束[[以巴冲突|以巴冲突]]是恢复埃、以两国关系的先决条件<ref name="Ahram"/>。

==荣誉==
* The State Encouragemental Prize in Engineering Sciences from the Academy of Scientific Research and Technology in 1987 and 1997
* First Class Medal of Excellence，[[穆巴拉克|穆巴拉克]]授予，1995<ref name="purdue"/>
* Cairo University Incentive Award for Scientific Excellence in Engineering in 1997 
* Egyptian State Prize in Engineering Sciences, 1997
* Excellence Award in Engineering，[[普渡大學|普渡大學]], 2005 <ref name="purdue"/>
* Man of the Year Award ([[拉菲克·哈里里|拉菲克·哈里里]]奖), [[贝鲁特|贝鲁特]]，2006
* Fellow of the [[Chartered_Institute_of_Logistics_and_Transport_in_the_UK|Chartered Institute of Logistics and Transport in the UK]] in 2007
* Certificate of Merit，[[开罗大学|开罗大学]] in the Celebration of Scientists Day in 1988 and 1998 <ref name="purdue"/>

